      tags: ["Economics", "Politics"],
      readTime: 21,
      releaseDate: "December 2nd, 2024",
      isRead: true,
      type: "Site",
      content:
        "The Next School of Economic Thought On the history of Economic Thought and it's next step forward Economics Politics",
    },
    {
